{
  "stem": "490.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, he was-- you wouldn't believe it, but the profession my-- my brother took over from my father-- he used to make ropes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to make-- Like, in Poland, they-- they-- they-- they didn't have-- the-- the mechanism wasn't-- weren't mechanized.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everything was horse and-- horses and buggies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the horses had to pull the wagon with two ropes on the side tied onto the wagon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was a quite a popular business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, they used to-- also used to make ropes for-- those heavy ropes to catch-- to pull the nets, to catch fish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was a very complicated or popular business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my brother took over this business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was hoping that I would continue with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I hated this thing, because it was always work outside in-- in 30 below zero, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very-- And-- and, of course, when I got home from school, and the next day, you know, I-- I told my principal that I couldn't, you know-- why I didn't do my homework, maybe.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe I wasn't as sharp as I-- he expected me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I told him that I had to help my brother with his-- excuse me-- blasted kind of work, which it was very uncomfortable, especially for a youngster.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they didn't have too much problem to convince me to leave this place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the only thing-- my sister, which she raised me-- she got married, and she moved to the next city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, it was next to Chelm, which everybody knows about the Chelm Jewish folklore stories comes of jokes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chelm was a very lovely city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To me, if I look back, Chelm was like the San Francisco of-- of the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
